Class GuiManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • mainGui.GuiManager
  • public class GuiManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Control center for the core GUI functionality, primarily acting as a middle man between the main screen and content panes.
    Version:
    1.0, May 2019.
    Author:
